<b>Most Credit Cards</b><br>
On most credit cards, with the notable exception of the American Express card,
the credit card verification number can be found on the reverse side of the
card. The number is an extra three digits printed inside the signature area
after the credit card number.  This number is not embossed into the front of
the card - it only appears on the back.

</td><td valign=top>
